"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-06-paris-2024-olympics-brume-usoro-ochonogor-through-to-womens-long-jump-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Team Nigeria's trio of Ese Brume, Ruth Usoro and Prestina Ochonogor, have qualified for the women's long jump final at the ongoing 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9895858452122369, \"rank\": 0.008193028940259065, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 42, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ese_Brume\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ese Brume\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ese_Brume\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ese_Brume\"}, {\"begin\": 53, \"end\": 57, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruth_Pointer\", \"score\": 0.9943923617247423, \"rank\": 0.005639261142362171, \"text\": \"Ruth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruth_Pointer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ruth_Pointer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the first time three Nigerian will be competing in the final of the long jump event at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 197, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.999999422259119, \"rank\": 5.722599533239097e-07, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The trio will battle nine other athletes for medals in the final.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brume leapt to an automatic qualifying mark of 6.76m to book her spot in the final.\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 428, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Usoro qualified with a mark of 6.68m, while she claimed her spot with 6.65m.\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The final of the event will take place on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Transfer: Chelsea set to announce arrival of new striker for Maresca  Transfer: He's top, amazing player - Caicedo hails departing Chelsea star  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's dismal performance worries enthusiasts  Paris 2024 Olympics: D'Tigress' Wakama wins Best Coach award  Paris 2024 Olympics: Brume vows to  bounce back from disappointing outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Sports Minister apologises to Nigerians after disastrous outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Team Nigeria officially finishes without single medal  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's last medal hope Reuben crashes out in Wrestling  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9975344723020962, \"rank\": 0.0024714666529112063, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 700, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9975344723020962, \"rank\": 0.0024714666529112063, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9895858452122369, \"rank\": 0.008193028940259065, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"htt